    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scanner Sombre》是一款紧张刺激的 3d 恐怖洞穴探索游戏，在游戏中，压抑的黑暗成为你最大的敌人。寂静中只有回声和迟疑的脚步声，营造出令人不寒而栗的紧张气氛，而看不见的未知则让你提心吊胆。这款游戏融合了心理恐怖和探索精神，挑战你如何在激光雷达扫描仪照亮的隐秘世界中航行。这款身临其境的冒险游戏出自《监狱建筑师》的创作者之手，利用光影营造出一种令人毛骨悚然的美丽体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/475190/extras/41058a1607d52b972cc5548ca784ff40.webp?t=1739424284\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/475190/extras/bda4d794f5e25ccd337953b772ed3ee5.poster.avif?t=1739424284\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/475190/extras/bda4d794f5e25ccd337953b772ed3ee5.webm?t=1739424284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/475190/extras/bda4d794f5e25ccd337953b772ed3ee5.mp4?t=1739424284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在《Scanner Sombre》中，激光雷达扫描仪是你的生命线。有了这一创新工具，你就能将光线投射到深渊，慢慢绘制出周围洞穴的地图，从而揭开不为人知的秘密。随着寂静的逼近和阴影的扭曲，扫描仪的彩色光束将揭开隐藏在黑暗中的危险和不可告人的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/475190/extras/703f2c4bbe2de0353b9ac7d78dda87c8.webp?t=1739424284\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/475190/extras/6ec8f2e40d2f40ac505a4821d74f3adf.poster.avif?t=1739424284\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/475190/extras/6ec8f2e40d2f40ac505a4821d74f3adf.webm?t=1739424284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/475190/extras/6ec8f2e40d2f40ac505a4821d74f3adf.mp4?t=1739424284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scanner Sombre》采用了一种引人注目的视觉风格，围绕鲜艳的彩虹色点云展开，灵感来自工业激光雷达扫描。玩家使用手持扫描仪逐步揭示环境，彩色编码点有助于感知深度。这种独特的非人类美学营造出阴森恐怖的氛围，增强了探索体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/475190/extras/dce21cef7dd793345193f368218a9362.webp?t=1739424284\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/475190/extras/e14e48da21f28259303fa3be3eff6031.poster.avif?t=1739424284\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/475190/extras/e14e48da21f28259303fa3be3eff6031.webm?t=1739424284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/475190/extras/e14e48da21f28259303fa3be3eff6031.mp4?t=1739424284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Scanner Sombre》中，故事通过环境巧妙地展开，洞穴中隐藏着被遗忘的历史的蛛丝马迹。在你探索的过程中，过去的遗迹、奇怪的符号和阴森恐怖的残留物暗示着更深层、更黑暗的叙事。每前进一步，都会让你一点一点揭开谜底。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/475190/extras/b3d3fbb9b0c5a5e9a1436825dd9f669f.webp?t=1739424284\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Introversion Software 自 2001 年起开始开发游戏，推出了《Uplink》、《Darwinia》、《Multiwinia》、《监狱建筑师》、《Scanner Sombre》等广受好评的游戏，以及最新发布的《The Last Starship》。Introversion 获得了评论界和商业界的双重成功，并获得了多个奖项，包括 IGF 大奖（《达尔文尼亚》）和英国 BAFTA 最佳持续性游戏奖（《监狱建筑师》）。 他们的游戏已在全球售出 400 多万份。</p>",
